aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 19, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cyp1671087505679.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cyp1671087505679.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cyp1671087505679.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cyp1671087505679\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the minimum allowed TLS protocol version.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">min_tls_version | min_tls_v = {1.0 | 1.1 | <u class=\"ph u\">1.2</u>| 1.3}</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cyp1671087505679__section_hzl_21s_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1099659e56\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use this setting to downgrade the minimum TLS protocol version. Even if you specify a lower\n\t\t\t\tprotocol version, OpenSSL still attempts to connect to the highest protocol\n\t\t\t\tfirst.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cyp1671087505679__section_fbp_g1s_vvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1099659e65\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Uniface uses TLS version 1.2 as the default level, since older protocols are currently\n\t\t\t\tconsidered unsafe. You can override this setting when there is a need to connect to\n\t\t\t\tlegacy systems that do not support TLS v1.2.</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\" id=\"cyp1671087505679__example_z3v_xwj_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1099659e74\">Example: Downgrading TLS to version 1.0</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following assignment settings permit all supported TLS versions starting from v1.0, such\n\t\t\t\tas v1.0, v1.1, v1.2, and v1.3.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104cyp1671087505679_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"cyp1671087505679__codeblock_cpb_dzj_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;client.asn\n[NET_SETTINGS]\nCheckClient=<strong class=\"ph b\">min_tls_version=1.0</strong>, client_certificate=clcert.crt, %\\client_key=clkey.key, client_key_password=pas5Word</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526675\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526675\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "min_tls_version Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 19, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the minimum allowed TLS protocol version. min_tls_version | min_tls_v = {1.0 | 1.1 | 1.2 | 1.3} Use Use this setting to downgrade the minimum TLS protocol version. Even if you specify a lower protocol version, OpenSSL still attempts to connect to the highest protocol first. Description Uniface uses TLS version 1.2 as the default level, since older protocols are currently considered unsafe. You can override this setting when there is a need to connect to legacy systems that do not support TLS v1.2. Example: Downgrading TLS to version 1.0 The following assignment settings permit all supported TLS versions starting from v1.0, such as v1.0, v1.1, v1.2, and v1.3. Explain this code ;client.asn [NET_SETTINGS] CheckClient= min_tls_version=1.0 , client_certificate=clcert.crt, %\\client_key=clkey.key, client_key_password=pas5Word Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}